Install instructions:
---------------------
make
optionally copy gangbangrc.sample to ~/.gangbangrc
run binary


Known Bugs:
-----------
- weird segfaulting on window size changes
- weird segfaulting when working with menus
- weirdest segfaulting with menus and window size changes in combination
- menu gets overpainted if underlaying areas are refreshed (songchange, etc...)

Note: this piece of software is quite untested right now. Don't wonder if you
find any bugs or missing features, and don't hesitate to report them.
